description: This file implements a C source module for the Advanced Networking Service Container (ANSC), specifically the 'Ansc Module Container Object'. It provides a function to retrieve an associated interface object, 'AnscMcoGetQueryIfObject'. The code includes license information, module description, and a single getter function.

methods.name: ANSC_HANDLE AnscMcoGetQueryIfObject(ANSC_HANDLE hThisObject)
methods.description: Retrieves the 'hQueryIfObject' member of the 'PANSC_MODULE_CONTAINER_OBJECT', which is the handle to the query interface object.
